// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0562 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 9b6a1f99-0b62-5827-abbd-440a3778a635

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
